                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl text-white font-bold mb-1">Tier 1</h3>
            <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[#D20202] mb-1">App Audit & Security Readiness</h4>
            <div class="text-2xl text-white font-bold mb-1">$4,500</div>
            <p class="text-xs text-white">One-time investment</p>
          </div>

          <div class="mb-4">
            <h5 class="font-semibold text-[#D20202] mb-2 text-sm">Transformation:</h5>
            <p class="text-white text-xs mb-3">
              Clarity on vulnerabilities, performance risks, and architectural flaws before launch
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="flex-1">
            <h5 class="font-semibold text-[#D20202] mb-2 text-sm">Includes:</h5>
            <ul class="space-y-1.5 text-xs text-white">
              <li class="flex items-start font-black">
                <svg class="w-3 h-3 text-[#D20202] mt-0.5 mr-2 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                </svg>
                Full-stack technical audit (backend, API, frontend)
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start font-black">
                <svg class="w-3 h-3 text-[#D20202] mt-0.5 mr-2 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                </svg>
                Security checklist (OWASP top 10, Auth, GDPR/PII flags)
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start font-black">
                <svg class="w-3 h-3 text-[#D20202] mt-0.5 mr-2 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
